<a href="http://gain.fas.usda.gov/Recent%20GAIN%20Publications/Citrus%20Annual_Pretoria_South%20Africa%20-%20Republic%20of_12-11-2012.pdf " target="_self">http://gain.fas.usda.gov/Recent%20GAIN%20Publications/Citrus%20Annual_Pr...</a></p><p><i>Freshfruitportal.com</i>, “Spanish growers group calls to control South African citrus imports”, 11 March 2013</p><p>
